item.title: Colin Firth & Pierce Brosnan & Stellan Skarsgard & Amanda Seyfried & Meryl Streep - Our Last Summer - Key of G - Fredonia Ukulele Club
item.description: Play along video for the song Our Last Summer by Colin Firth & Pierce Brosnan & Stellan Skarsgard & Amanda Seyfried & Meryl Streep from the channel Fredonia Ukulele Club. Chords used in the song: Am, Bm, C, D, D7, Em, G.
